  • Type Parameters:
    I - Input type of model produced by this trainer.
    O - Output type of model produced by this trainer.

    OW - Output type of model produced by wrapped trainer.
    M - Type of model produced by wrapped model.
    L - Type of labels.

    public class AdaptableDatasetTrainer<I,O,IW,OW,M extends IgniteModel<IW,OW>,L>
extends DatasetTrainer<AdaptableDatasetModel<I,O,IW,OW,M>,L>
    Type used to adapt input and output types of wrapped DatasetTrainer. Produces model which is composition of form before `andThen` wMdl `andThen` after where wMdl is model produced by wrapped trainer.
